article.description: — Luke Sutherland's 24 points helped Le Moyne defeat Dartmouth 80-54 on Saturday.
article.headline: Sutherland scores 24 in Le Moyne's 80-54 win against Dartmouth
article.linkText: Sutherland scores 24 in Le Moyne's 80-54 win against Dartmouth
article.story: SYRACUSE, N.Y. -- — Luke Sutherland's 24 points helped Le Moyne defeat Dartmouth 80-54 on Saturday. Sutherland was 10-of-15 shooting (4 for 8 from 3-point range) for the Dolphins (4-7). Kaiyem Cleary scored 19 points and added six rebounds. Nathan McClure was 3-of-5 shooting (2 for 4 from 3-point range) to finish with eight points, while adding 12 rebounds. Nikola Dimitrijevic led the way for the Big Green (3-7) with 12 points. Jaren Johnson added 12 points and three steals for Dartmouth. In addition, Romeo Myrthil finished with nine points, six rebounds and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
